title: Print, "Kasteel de Hooge Vuursche", 20th century
creditline: Museum purchase from Sarah Cooper-Hewitt Fund
description: Triangular luggage label in red, white, blue, yellow, black, with a traveler in traditional Dutch costume loaded down with golf clubs, tulips and much baggage. Text, in a wavy cartouche lower margin: KASTEEL DE HOOGE VUURSCHE; left border: BAARN; right border: HOLLAND
